# Product Brief

## Product Name

SecureBenefits Mobile App

## Product Type

Enterprise benefits administration SaaS mobile application

## Target Users

- Employees accessing benefits information
- HR administrators supporting employee benefits
- Implementation teams configuring client environments
- Support teams troubleshooting access issues

## Problem Statement

Enterprise clients need a secure, reliable mobile benefits experience that protects sensitive employee data while remaining easy to access and use. Current implementation challenges often include unclear SSO requirements, inconsistent timeout behavior, and limited release-readiness documentation.

## Business Goals

- Improve security and compliance readiness.
- Reduce implementation delays.
- Improve client confidence during onboarding.
- Increase consistency across enterprise deployments.

## User Goals

- Employees want quick and secure access to benefits information.
- HR admins want fewer access-related support issues.
- Implementation teams want clearer requirements and repeatable workflows.
- Engineering and QA need testable acceptance criteria.

## Scope

### In Scope

- Session timeout behavior
- SSO setup workflow
- API requirement examples
- UAT test planning
- Release readiness checklist

### Out of Scope

- Full application redesign
- Real production code
- Employer-specific data
- Client-specific configurations
